                        <tr>
                                <td colspan="2"><span class="postbody">Most everything has already been said but I saw a few GLARING errors that id like to talk about.
<br />

<br />

<br />
Practice in HoH and follow these rules:
<br />
1. Keep the mob you are fighting ROOTED AT ALL TIMES.
<br />
2. Do not slow the mob you are fighting unless necessary. 
<br />
3. Do not haste your pet if you are soloing.
<br />
4. Use insanity and slow to keep the fight as close as possible.
<br />
5. Make your pet win by the tiniest margin then kill your pet.
<br />
6. Keep yourself sowed at ALL times.
<br />
7. DONT  RE-USE PETS SOLOING.
<br />

<br />

<br />
Do this and you will get the hang of it soon</span><span class="postbody"><br />_________________<br /><img src="http://strike9.com/file.ashx?path=%2fVizier%2ffullsize%2fVizierSig4.jpg" border="0" />
<br />

<br />
One name...many faces.
<br />
-Vizier, 65 Coercer of Fennin Ro</span><span class="gensmall"></span></td>
