                        <tr>
                                <td colspan="2"><span class="postbody">The rules i posted are for hoh where the mobs re perfectly paired up and evenly matched. No reason whatsover to haste and in fact its going to lead to worse exp overall. If you re-use over and over it takes 33 percent exp every kill. My way it takes 33% exp every other kill at worst.
<br />

<br />
And yes you can break charm and kill pet but thats a hassle and can sometimes cost you more time and mana than you would save if you just let pet kill. With the roots and the nukes and the insane mob regen i usually dont mess with it in HoH. Just let pet kill, the wipe pet in a nuke or two and your ready for then next round. Clean simple and effecient.
<br />

<br />

<br />
I will haste pet when soloing in places like poWater or Fire, or if i have a ranger/druid partner. but thats not what I was talking about. And that strat in hoh is better exp than Fire or Water per hour easily anyways.</span><span class="postbody"><br />_________________<br /><img src="http://strike9.com/file.ashx?path=%2fVizier%2ffullsize%2fVizierSig4.jpg" border="0" />
