                        <tr>
                                <td colspan="2"><span class="postbody">Best thing about this whole forum is all of us "know it all" uber Coercers can do a seemingly straight forward thing such as Charm soloing so incredibly different. I almost always find a new tactic/strategy out there when I review these forums, and this section is no different. HoH basement..SE, is simply the best place to gain xp and try out a different charm play. I have always used one pet to clear the other 5, but I also like my afk's and this gives me time to do so between spawns. I find PoTactics good for this as well..wait on piggy in an incredibly safe point inside SW camp...and then charm any of the others to kill him, squish pet and /afk until piggy pops again. Piggy is rootable/slowable/and non-summoning...10K per hour is minimal.
<br />

<br />
But gear is one thing I am sure we can all agree on...difficult encounters become trivial with the right equipment. When you can cast quicker from farther away, with less mana used and quicker regen..well it all becomes soo much smoother and less stressful. Find or make groups to camp the gear you choose...then farm pp for the gear that is saleable...but when set up correctly the advantage to us is extreme.
<br />

<br />
Tayemm Initio
<br />
Coercer of Mith Marr</span><span class="postbody"></span><span class="gensmall"></span></td>
