                                <td colspan="2"><span class="postbody">All this is great advice but I dont see one of my most important steps in charm soloing.. Pet guard. Put guard on pet where you are pulling to and sit far away as you can while fight is going on. This is important because you dont want your pet following you inbetween fights. He will stay a nice comfy distance at all times. 
<br />

<br />
As far as haste/not haste debate, I always haste with epic, mana free faster kills. If I'm paying attention at all times he's never gonna catch me when it breaks.
<br />

<br />
PoV is awesome place to charm solo btw.
